snippet.title: slonderman release trailer
snippet.description:
My final TE game, Slonderman, is out! Hope you enjoy! 

Gamejolt: https://gamejolt.com/games/slondy/340555
Itch.io: https://deerpy.itch.io/slenderman

Game description: 
Wait, Hold on! There is a story to this madness! I dunno, er... You fell out a helicopter and landed (and somehow survived) in Slonder's forest. Slonder then told you to collect his fanart or he would kill you and not let you go free.
Now download the game and play it!
